{"tid":2000363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"何潔思你好嘢! 我當你好姐妹你就呃我錢，夠膽就做一世縮頭烏龜咪返香港","createTime":"2020-05-03T22:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T07:26:33.000Z","uid":318975,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"93c80ec52ccc64b1e0870c206aea5eccbfb1c3e7","tid":2000363,"uid":318975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T22:44:52.000Z","msg":"上個post講咗佢點唔還錢，宜家就擺相<br />\n雖然只呃我一萬，走財務公司一萬八。<br />\n但都想大家警惕呢個人，第2就係唔好亂借錢比朋友，唔好好似我咁低能智障去信一個朋友。<br />\n<br />\n何潔思 Jessie Ho R547xxxx<br />\n2001年3月14日 <br />\n160cm 70kg<br />\n密碼: 碌唔易死 狗易死狗<br />\nwe柒: hongkong_girl_13<br />\n喺寶血女子中學讀到中三，中四開始讀IVE design，讀1年就讀唔掂日日喺屋企hea。<br />\n<br />\n冇錢就問我請唔請佢食飯，厚面皮到喊。<br />\n返過中環KFC同McDonald's，不過借我錢之後日日打機冇返工(有2次下午打比佢，佢仲打緊機)<br />\n聽講宜家為咗躲債返咗四川(唔知真假)<br />\n<br />\n賤到學生錢你都呃，比咗半年時間你仍然一蚊唔還，仲要日日玩鳩我話聽日還後日還。然後一到限期夜晚11點幾就諸多藉口話還唔還錢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3j0KFG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3j0KFG.jpg&h=f9da62c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nso8Ty2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNso8Ty2.jpg&h=3bda587f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KJEfNo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KJEfNo.jpg&h=1a052aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ffidkd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfidkd4.jpg&h=3e2acc97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwBiwkL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwBiwkL.jpg&h=8f834c5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mj8EfNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmj8EfNr.jpg&h=cbd338ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VomeO7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVomeO7s.jpg&h=33b40b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWd5bkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWd5bkO.jpg&h=3eb9b833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cf9LVNu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCf9LVNu.jpg&h=d54855a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45wN87v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45wN87v.jpg&h=72358c19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PnnhM6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPnnhM6A.jpg&h=7e8c96fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EctTQ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EctTQ7.jpg&h=70eecefe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個人表面支持香港運動但實則純粹po ig呃like, 睇佢參加軍事夏令營就知咩事。<br />\n中國人果然係呃錢高手，冇文化冇學歷冇社經地位，要用呃錢去生存。<br />\n希望你真係返咗大陸，咪再扮香港人😉"},{"pid":"fbc79510beeb06b0f1521d06ca95993942a72d3d","tid":2000363,"uid":189109,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T22:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/28/Lf2.gif/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F28%2FLf2.gif%2F&h=e90235ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a7ac5784245d40b7649fbe7e999417ddee4d780","tid":2000363,"uid":38518,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T22:55:49.000Z","msg":"屌你呢啲就咁多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55306020974ea89c5533754efecd0875a91c3a12","tid":2000363,"uid":274789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T23:13:23.000Z","msg":"講還講唔使貼圖嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fc8efc0aa7a0b10100cf068b22282d5eff085c","tid":2000363,"uid":88578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply